        <div n="P0040601">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Neither is it meerly my own private Opinion, that Politeness is the firmest Foundation upon which Loyalty can be supported: For, thus happily sings the never-to-be-too-much-admired <ref target="#spp-P0040601-footnote-headnote-1">1</ref><note n="1" xml:id="spp-P0040601-footnote-headnote-1" place="foot"><hi rend="italics">It is erroneously printed in the </hi>London<hi rend="italics"> Edition, Mr</hi>. Stephen Duck</note> Lord <hi rend="italics">H</hi>────, in his truly sublime Poem, called, <hi rend="italics">Loyalty defined</hi>.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-P0040601-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-P0040601-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="italics">Who's not polite, for the Pretender, is;</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-P0040601-line-2" n="2"><hi rend="italics">A Jacobite, I know him by his Phizz</hi>,</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
